Still sulking, are you?

284
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:30,840
I'm not as petty as you.

285
00:14:31,510 --> 00:14:32,390
I don't hold grudges.

286
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,160
Come on, open the door.

287
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:42,040
Hey.

288
00:14:44,670 --> 00:14:45,510
Heng.

289
00:14:45,980 --> 00:14:48,210
Don't tell me you're getting used
to this prison cart.

290
00:14:48,300 --> 00:14:50,230
Does this give you that much joy?

291
00:14:51,210 --> 00:14:52,950
I only locked you up for a while.

292
00:14:53,480 --> 00:14:54,390
Hardly a big deal.

293
00:14:54,390 --> 00:14:55,600
You know exactly what I mean.

294
00:15:01,160 --> 00:15:03,920
I lead my 200 brothers to share
wealth and glory.

295
00:15:04,510 --> 00:15:05,510
Why wouldn't I be happy?

296
00:15:06,920 --> 00:15:07,870
Happy?

297
00:15:08,480 --> 00:15:09,320
Is that it?

298
00:15:10,270 --> 00:15:11,870
There's no greater joy than this.

299
00:15:12,170 --> 00:15:14,420
But your greater joy will bring harm
to many more lives.

300
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:15,280
Wang Heng.

301
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:17,670
You just want to drive away my men

302
00:15:17,670 --> 00:15:18,870
so you can charge ahead alone

303
00:15:18,870 --> 00:15:19,710
and claim the Qilin?

304
00:15:19,720 --> 00:15:20,750
If all of your men

305
00:15:21,080 --> 00:15:22,630
were to die in Chang'an,

306
00:15:23,080 --> 00:15:24,180
would you still be pleased?

307
00:15:29,010 --> 00:15:30,860
I merely saw through your scheme,

308
00:15:31,840 --> 00:15:32,910
yet you cursed my men

309
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:35,440
only for the Qilin?

310
00:15:36,270 --> 00:15:37,320
Listen.

311
00:15:37,750 --> 00:15:38,840
This is no curse.

312
00:15:39,030 --> 00:15:40,080
It's the Mandate of Heaven.

313
00:15:40,670 --> 00:15:41,600
All of these men but you

314
00:15:42,390 --> 00:15:43,600
will die

315
00:15:43,760 --> 00:15:44,640
because of you.

316
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:56,790
Wang, come on.

317
00:16:01,480 --> 00:16:03,080
(Chamberlain Gong
admonished the Duke)

318
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:05,320
(and had over 50 sent back.)

319
00:16:05,430 --> 00:16:06,440
(The process was altered,)

320
00:16:06,590 --> 00:16:08,010
(yet the outcome remained the same.)

321
00:16:08,510 --> 00:16:09,820
(History has not changed at all.)

322
00:16:29,760 --> 00:16:32,160
♪Watch the storm;
hear the night rain fall♪

323
00:16:32,160 --> 00:16:33,760
♪Till the light of dawn♪

324
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:35,480
♪A truth that cannot be spoken♪

325
00:16:36,160 --> 00:16:37,840
♪Right and wrong matter♪

326
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:39,960
♪Yet I can't make the right choice♪

327
00:16:40,160 --> 00:16:41,600
♪The lost player in the game♪

328
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:44,960
♪Made a move by a twist of fate♪

329
00:16:44,960 --> 00:16:47,480
♪The way back is lost,
leaving nowhere to return♪

330
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:50,720
♪Borrow the endless cycles♪

331
00:16:51,280 --> 00:16:54,760
♪To fight for the most perfect outcome♪

332
00:16:55,520 --> 00:16:57,880
♪How to trace the threads
and follow cause and effect♪

333
00:16:57,880 --> 00:17:01,640
♪Seeking a strategy without flaw♪

334
00:17:01,920 --> 00:17:06,560
♪How to break free
from this fated yet unforeseen lock♪

335
00:17:06,720 --> 00:17:11,760
♪To live so as to shake the world♪

336
00:17:12,120 --> 00:17:16,240
♪With this journey,
I gain a fiercer edge♪

337
00:17:16,360 --> 00:17:18,440
♪I've planned
before I act countless times♪

338
00:17:18,520 --> 00:17:24,880
♪Fatal danger turned into a jest♪

339
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:29,200
♪Through this road,
I watch the endless rise and fall♪

340
00:17:29,240 --> 00:17:31,320
♪In the chapters lie ages
of decay and bloom♪

341
00:17:31,320 --> 00:17:33,240
♪Let us meet again♪

342
00:17:33,280 --> 00:17:38,440
♪One hurried path, and one at ease♪
